  "description": "Tom and Terry are coworkers who find themselves with a shared secret after an evening together on the weekend. Now it's Monday... will this secret break them or strengthen their bond?",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Clayton James-Plamondon &amp; Erin Leflar<br/><strong>Director</strong>: Sue Goberdhan<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Clayton James-Plamondon, Erin Leflar, Mitchell Kinsella<br/><strong>Stage Manager</strong>: Emily Rittammer<br/>",
